.SS Parameters:
.IP "\fBinput\fR=\fIname\fR" 4m
.br
Name of raster file to be linked
.IP "\fBsource\fR=\fIname\fR" 4m
.br
Name of non\-file GDAL data source
.IP "\fBoutput\fR=\fIname\fR \fB[required]\fR" 4m
.br
Name for output raster map
